it.polimi.se2019.server.model.game

Class Cubes

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.model.game.Cubes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Cubes
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Cubes class represent a collection of maximum 9 cubes: 3 of each colour. It has three int fields: reds, yellows and blues indicating the number of cubes for each color.
    Author:
    mattiamassarini,merklind.
